# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Public-portfolio .gitignore
# Goal: the repo GitHub shows = README + docs + notebooks + figures
#       + results + data pointer. Everything heavy/internal stays local.
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Raw experiment dump (1.5 GB) — curated subset lives in results/
log/

# Trained model artifacts (large binaries)
*.pkl
*.npy
*.joblib

# Raw competition data — see data/README.md for how to obtain
public_train.csv
public_test.csv
data/*.csv
data/*.tsv

# Course-provided material (redistribution-restricted)
student_guide.pdf

# Redundant local working copies of the original notebooks
# (clean versions are committed under notebooks/)
final/
drill06 final/

# Internal drafts / superseded files (not for public view)
README_PORTFOLIO.md
docs/_design/
docs/README_ko_legacy.md

# Duplicate (canonical copy lives in results/)
docs/experiments_master.csv

# Session scratch / verification artifacts
__perm_test.txt
_gitcheck/
__mvtest*

# Python / notebook cruft
.ipynb_checkpoints/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.DS_Store
.venv/
env/
